The Mera depicter in "Aquaman" shared details of their marital issues in a statement revealed during her husband's libel trial against British tabloid The Sun on Monday, July 20.    "He accused me of having affairs with each of my co-stars, movie after movie: Eddie Redmayne, James Franco, Jim Sturgess, Kevin Costner, Liam Hemsworth, Billy Bob Thornton, Channing Tatum," Amber said. snippet.title: Amber Heard Called James Franco a 'Rapist,' According to Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
not biased to any side! ✌
hit that subscribe button!✌
Amber Heard Called James Franco a 'Rapist,' According to Johnny Depp
Amber Heard allegedly called James Franco a “rapist,” her ex husband Johnny Depp apparently said in court today while being questioned by lawyers.

During his libel case against a UK tabloid, he was asked about the period of time where Amber agreed to star in 2015′s The Adderall Diaries alongside James Franco. Johnny said he was “shocked” when she signed on to make the film and admitted it made him feel “jealous.”

“It shocked me she was suddenly so friendly and happy with him,” Johnny said on the stand today (via the Evening Standard). “She told me many things that were very very negative about Mr Franco, that he had tried to kiss her and made sexual advances towards her on the previous film they had made together. She said he was a creep and a rapist. She said he was quite aggressive in his advances towards her.”

The lawyer then clarified Johnny‘s use of the word “rapist,” “You have made an 
extremely important statement just now.”

Johnny replied, “It’s just a word that came out for the actions of Mr Franco, as described to me by Ms Heard, which were sexual advances, him leaning over and saying I’m going to kiss you. She had to sort of run from the advances at one point, that he was kind of non-stop, she felt he was creepy and rapey so I said a rapist.”

snippet.title: Involucran a James Franco en la demanda de Johnny Depp contra Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp y Amber Heard han estado en guerra desde 2016 cuando ella le solicitó el divorcio y lo acusó de violencia doméstica, sin embargo el actor ahora le exige 50 millones de dólares por haberlo difamado.

Ahora los abogados del actor han citado a James Franco para que de la versión del día que compartió con ella un ascensor, ya que de acuerdo con declaraciones de la actriz un día antes Deep le pegó, causándole varios hematomas en el rostro, según informó la revista People.

Asimismo el portal estadounidense The Blast, reveló un video en donde aparecen Franco y Heard en un elevador, aunque no se les ve el rostro, ya que ambos están agachados.

La fecha de esta grabación es del 22 de mayo del 2016, justo un día después de la pelea que terminó con la relación de esta pareja.

Antes de su separación, Heard levantó varias denuncias en contra del actor por maltrato físico.

Se convertía en una persona delirante y violenta y cuando consumía alcohol y drogas me pegaba”. Amber Heard.

También confesó que Franco era uno de los principales causantes de sus peleas y del enojo el actor le lanzaba objetos y la insultaba.

Por su parte, Deep niega este comportamiento violento y por eso ha decidido acusarla de difamación. Además asegura que la actriz le fue infiel con Elon Musk, fundador de Tesla mientras todavía estaban casados.

snippet.title: James Franco & Amber Heard Bring 'The Adderall Diaries' to Tribeca Film Festival 2015
snippet.description:
James Franco & Amber Heard Bring 'The Adderall Diaries' to Tribeca Film Festival 2015
James Franco suits while posing next to Amber Heard at the premiere of their new film The Adderall Diaries during the 2015 Tribeca Film Festival at BMCC Tribeca PAC on Thursday night (April 16) in New York City.

The duo was joined on the red carpet by their co-stars Christian Slater and Cynthia Nixon.

Based on the bestselling memoir by Stephen Elliott, The Adderall Diaries is the story of an author (Franco) paralyzed by writer’s block and an escalating drug dependency who is sucked down the rabbit hole of a high-profile murder case.

FYI: Amber is wearing Stella McCartney.

As a writer stymied by past success, writers block, substance abuse, relationship problems and a serious set of father issues, Elliott's cracked-out chronicle of a bizarre murder trial amounts to less than the sum of its parts. Not long into the 2007 trial of programmer Hans Reiser, accused of murdering his wife, the defendant's friend Sean Sturgeon obliquely confessed to several murders (though not the murder of Reiser's wife). Elliott, caught up in the film-ready twist and his tenuous connection to Sturgeon (they share a BDSM social circle), makes a gonzo record of the proceedings. The result is a scattered, self-indulgent romp through the mind of a depressive narcissist obsessed with his insecurities and childhood traumas.

snippet.title: Johnny Depp Gets Elon Musk’s Help Testifying Against Amber Heard !
snippet.description:
Divorce is never easy, and when it comes to celebrity divorce, public attention is added to the whole nightmare that follows the process. Of course, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s split is certainly no exception. Even though their legal battle has already lasted years, there's a little chance that new participants of the case, like Tesla CEO Elon Musk and actor James Franco, end up testifying in the court case against Amber Heard?
According to court documents obtained by Us Weekly, James Franco and Elon Musk were subpoenaed on October 26, 2021. They were ordered to “produce the books, record, electronically stored information and tangible things designated and described” — including “verbal conversations, telephone calls, letters, emails, memoranda and reports” — by January 17, 2022. As we have already spoken in details about James Franco being dragged to the case in the previous video (if you haven’t seen it, you definitely should), in this episode we are going to reveal all the details about Elon Musk’s who once challenged Johnny Depp to a cage fight. 
Johnny Depp’s legal team is interested in speaking with Elon Mus kand James Franco because they may have a really important information that can help the case going. Here is an official Adam Waldman’s (JD’s lawyer) statement: “We are interested in James Franco and Elon Musk as fact witnesses because we have evidence they are men who saw Amber Heard’s face in the days and nights between when she claimed Mr. Depp smashed her in the face on May 21 and when she went to court with painted on ‘bruises’ to obtain temporary restraining order on May 27”.
The Tesla billionaire Elon Musk has been involved in Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s case once again and this time around his connection to Amber/Johnny drama is a little bit different than previously. In short, Elon Musk has been involved to the entire scandal because he dated Amber Heard after the former couple’s split. Elon was first dragged into the dispute last year when Johnny Depp issued subpoena against him. This was part from a separate legal battle between the former couple in the US. 
But what does Elon have to do with everything that happens on the first place? Well, Elon Musk and Amber Heard had a short-lived romance after her marriage to Johnny Depp collapsed in 2016. However, though JD repeatedly has alleged that Elon and Amber Heard were romantically involved while before their split. Elon Musk has always denied these claims and even joked last summer about settling things with Johnny Depp in a “cage fight” when his name kept coming up at the ongoing UK libel trial. 
Moreover, when Amber and JD’s relationship began to fall apart, Amber was trying to get a restraining order against Johnny Depp and when she decided to this, she shared her thoughts about it with Elon Musk. After she revealed him her thoughts, he offered to pay and provide her with 24-hour security. Moreover, the High Court was told that Elon Musk became a regular late-night visitor to Amber Heard monthly. And allegedly, it all started way back in 2015. And you probably remember that ‘triangle’ scandal, involving Elon Musk, Amber Heard and British supermodel Cara Delevingne.Well, so many views and opinions. Bit I want to know your thoughts about the entire situation! Do you think Elon Musk’s testimony will help Johnny Depp win the court case? Or the fact that Elon Musk will appear in court will make things only worse for the actor? Let me know your opinion in the comments section down below. And thanks for watching this video and don’t forget to hit that subscribe button and turn on a notification bell. Bye-bye.

snippet.title: BEYOND LIES Bande Annonce (James Franco, Amber Heard - Thriller, 2016)
snippet.description:
En manque d’inspiration pour son prochain roman, un écrivain s’intéresse de près au procès d’un meurtrier...
★ Les MEILLEURS Thrillers ICI ► https://goo.gl/Iow5yO
★ Abonne-toi à la chaine Youtube ► https://goo.gl/zqsTO4

En manque d’inspiration pour son prochain roman, Stephen Elliott s’intéresse de près au procès d’un meurtrier, dont il remet en cause la culpabilité. Il décide de mener sa propre enquête, au risque de faire ressurgir son passé sur lequel il avait pourtant tiré un trait. Son obsession pour la vérité dépasse rapidement l’enquête et le confronte à ses propres doutes, sur son père notamment qui l’a abandonné et qu’il n’a jamais pardonné.

BEYOND LIES Bande Annonce
Un film réalisé par Pamela Romanowsky 
Avec James Franco, Christian Slater, Amber Heard
Date de sortie au cinéma en France : 7 septembre 2016 en VOD
Genre : Drame, Action, Thriller
